# VidTwit - Full-Stack App | Live Link | React.js, Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, JWT, Tailwind

• Developed a YouTube and Twitter clone from scratch and Enhanced responsive design and a 30% reduction in
average page load times

• Implemented Cloudinary for efficient image and media management, handling over 1,000 media uploads seamlessly,
also Integrated JWT for secure authentication, ensuring user data protection.

• Managed MongoDB/Mongoose for robust data handling, supporting over 10,000 user accounts, Conducted
extensive API testing with Postman, ensuring reliability and performance